---
const title = "Product Photography";
---

<section class="food-intro">
  <h2 class="food-intro__title">{title}</h2>

  <p class="food-intro__tagline">
    Make your packaged products, bottles and hero items look as good online as they do on the shelf.
  </p>

  <div class="food-intro__content">
    <p class="food-intro__body">
      As a Perth product photographer, we produce high-impact visuals for ecommerce, retail,
      packaged goods, food and beverage brands, skincare, candles and lifestyle products. From
      clean conversion-focused packshots to styled scenes, we help your products stand out.
    </p>

    <p class="food-intro__body">
      If your brand also needs supporting visuals or a strong online presence, you can combine
      this service with our
      <a href="/perth-food-photography/">Food Photography</a> or
      <a href="/website-development/">Website Development</a>
      to keep your product storytelling consistent across every channel.
    </p>
  </div>

  <a href="/contact/" class="food-intro__cta">
    Ready to level up your product photos?
  </a>
</section>

<style>
  :root {
    --text-color: #fef8eb;
    /* Deep warm charcoal for high contrast against cream text */
    --bg-color-premium: #232220; 
  }

  .food-intro {
    background-color: var(--bg-color-premium);
    color: var(--e-global-color-primary, var(--text-color));
    /* Added significant vertical padding for a "breathing" editorial look */
    padding: 100px 20px; 
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .food-intro__title {
    font-family: "Abril Fatface", serif;
    font-size: 60px; /* Increased size for impact */
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    color: var(--e-global-color-primary, var(--text-color));
    margin: 0 0 20px 0;
  }

  .food-intro__tagline {
    font-family: "Darker Grotesque", sans-serif;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 700; /* Bold to create hierarchy */
    text-transform: uppercase; /* Differentiates it from body text */
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    line-height: 1.4;
    color: var(--e-global-color-primary, var(--text-color));
    margin: 0 auto 40px auto; /* Spacing below tagline */
    max-width: 600px;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  /* Wrapper to constrain width of all paragraphs */
  .food-intro__content {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto 40px auto;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 25px; /* Consistent spacing between paragraphs */
  }

  .food-intro__body {
    font-family: "Darker Grotesque", sans-serif;
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 400;
    /* REMOVED ITALICS for readability */
    font-style: normal; 
    /* Increased line-height for elegance */
    line-height: 1.6; 
    color: var(--e-global-color-primary, var(--text-color));
    margin: 0;
  }

  .food-intro__body a {
    color: inherit;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 4px;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: opacity 0.3s;
  }

  .food-intro__body a:hover {
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  /* Styled as a Ghost Button */
  .food-intro__cta {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: "Darker Grotesque", sans-serif;
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: var(--e-global-color-primary, var(--text-color));
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 15px 40px;
    border: 1px solid var(--e-global-color-primary, var(--text-color));
    border-radius: 50px; /* Pill shape */
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    margin-top: 10px;
  }

  .food-intro__cta:hover {
    background-color: var(--e-global-color-primary, var(--text-color));
    color: var(--bg-color-premium); /* Invert colors on hover */
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  /* Responsive Adjustments */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .food-intro {
      padding: 60px 20px;
    }

    .food-intro__title {
      font-size: 42px;
    }

    .food-intro__tagline {
      font-size: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .food-intro__body {
      font-size: 19px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .food-intro__cta {
      font-size: 16px;
      padding: 12px 30px;
    }
  }
</style>
